{"type": "article", "id": 11536, "title": "Here 耳机", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-02T11:00:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 77, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702125746opGuHgWX8hrcmzP6.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t多普勒实验室最近推出了一款新型耳机，准确的说，是一款声音过滤器，其特点在于通过对现场的降噪，让使用者在听音乐时有身临其境的感觉，据介绍，耳机可以把听音乐的音量降低 12 分贝左右，并且将多频段声波降低到最合适的声压，让使用者有舒适的聆听体验，在嘈杂的环境中也能听见“高清”且舒服的声音。看来是带去草坪音乐节或是各种演唱会的好产品呢。目前，这款产品正在 Kickstarter 上众筹，预计 2015 年 12 月发货，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/dopplerlabs/here-active-listening-change-the-way-you-hear-the\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以支持他们。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135656cJhHTxlnQ7aNVXYs.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"614\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135656zoU0bCl7RDsaG1q9.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135656AJanotkP5uDdHGe9.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135657T7ZfNFqV4A3itp5z.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"419\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.51222494\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135657tywfFzSoL8HE6nZk.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"600\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.73349633\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}